definition: to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be
everything clear and in good order (idiom); neat and tidy

sentences.english: I've been keeping my room as neat as a pin, and the yard is always ship-shape.
sentences.chinese: 我一直保持房間井然有序，院子也是修得井井有條的。

sentences.english: The books are in orderly rows on the shelves.
sentences.chinese: 書整齊有序地排列在書架上。

sentences.english: The financial supervision is an important means for guaranteeing the orderly implementation of the financial activities.
sentences.chinese: 財務監督是保證財務活動有序進行的重要手段。

sentences.english: We will move forward with reform of the rural land management system in an orderly manner.
sentences.chinese: 有序推進農村土地管理制度改革。

sentences.english: The government should allow orderly dissolution for dying businesses.
sentences.chinese: 政府應該允許奄奄一息的企業有序地解體。

sentences.english: Ultimately, it is good for healthy and orderly development of Bayannur's small towns.
sentences.chinese: 最終促進巴彥淖爾市小城鎮健康有序的發展。

sentences.english: Get many empty seat, everyone orderly and sit down.
sentences.chinese: 上車後還有許多空座位，大家都有序的坐下了。

sentences.english: There are six households inhabiting in the building, compact and orderly.
sentences.chinese: 樓內住有六戶人家，家居緊湊，井然有序。

sentences.english: The ordered development of the Singapore society is always approved by the countries all over the world.
sentences.chinese: 新加坡社會的有序發展向來被世界各國所認同。

sentences.english: Non-silicon-based ordered mesoporous materials in recent years has been the emergence of a new research focus.
sentences.chinese: 非硅基有序介孔材料是近年來新興起的一個研究熱點。

sentences.english: The condition producing more order structure in crystal growth is discussed.
sentences.chinese: 討論了材料生長產生有序結構的條件。

sentences.english: Follows the cooperation system basic principle, to conduct a standard operation.
sentences.chinese: 遵循合作制基本原則，規範化有序運作。

sentences.english: No extraordinary disorder hinstanceens on the orderly circumference.
sentences.chinese: 在有序的界線上沒有發作不尋常的雜沓。

sentences.english: It was speculated that the morphology of ordered phase was needle-like.
sentences.chinese: 並推測有序相的形貌爲針狀。

sentences.english: Carries out and supervises the regular Guestroom Servicing Programme according to the established schedule.
sentences.chinese: 根據進度表開展有序的客房維修程序並監督之。

sentences.english: The Ukraine and Pakistan have also defaulted in orderly fashion.
sentences.chinese: 烏克蘭和巴基斯坦也曾發生過有序違約。
